Camoflage::

She smiled and started to eat the sweet energon.  She picked up a 
piece and walked over the console where Windlord was standing. She 
overheard him talk about the plague.  "I don't think we should 
worry.  I'm not sick.  If I was, I'd be rusted by now. And I'm not 
rusty. See?"  She twirled around on her toes.  "I'm not sick. So your 
not sick. Only worry is the pod. It's got rust spots. But don't 
worry. Once the pod rust away, we should be just fine. I hope."  She 
stood there sucking on the sweet energon.
